              <div class="space-y-6">
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-100">
                  Founded in 2020 in Arad, Romania, Jay Software emerged from a simple but powerful observation: most businesses lose thousands monthly to inefficient systems while their competitors pull ahead with smart automation.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-100">
                  We've seen companies struggle with vendor lock-in, forced workarounds, and generic solutions that don't fit their unique processes. That's why we built Jay Software with one clear mission: create custom software that pays for itself within 6 months through measurable ROI.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-100">
                  Today, we've helped over 50+ businesses transform their operations, generating millions in additional revenue and cost savings through strategic software development.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-center">
                <div>
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">50+</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Successful Projects</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">200%</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Average ROI</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">6 Months</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Avg. Payback</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400 mb-2">€2M+</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Client Savings</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Founder Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 via-slate-800 to-blue-900/20 relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Background Elements -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/10 to-purple-900/10"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative">
